@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = v2
    tmp = v1
    tmp = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.70 - v1 + 0.15)) * (wp.cos(tmp + 0.21) * wp.cos(v0 + 0.35)))
    tmp = 0.70
    v2 = v2
    data[tid] = v0
